{
    "chapterId": "Act01_Chapter04_Trial",
    "lines": [
        {
            "id": "line_3_0",
            "type": "dialogue",
            "speaker": "",
            "text": "你们回到中央审讯室。",
            "portrait": "null",
            "position": "center"
        },
        {
            "id": "line_3_1",
            "type": "dialogue",
            "speaker": "",
            "text": "你感觉周围的恶意不断袭来",
            "portrait": "null",
            "position": "center"
        },
        {
            "id": "line_3_2",
            "type": "dialogue",
            "speaker": "",
            "text": "率先发难的是A",
            "portrait": "null",
            "position": "center"
        },
        {
            "id": "line_3_3",
            "type": "dialogue",
            "speaker": "A",
            "text": "很可疑啊，看不懂的档案加上没有一点蛛丝马迹的房间",
            "portrait": "A/老囚1",
            "position": "right"
        },
        {
            "id": "line_3_4",
            "type": "dialogue",
            "speaker": "B",
            "text": "唯一的线索还是与C息息相关宗教项链，我只能认为房间是你精心布置后的样子",
            "portrait": "B/盗窃犯",
            "position": "right"
        },
        {
            "id": "line_3_5",
            "type": "dialogue",
            "speaker": "A",
            "text": "说起来之前都是你在指认啊。不知不觉陷入你的话术里去了",
            "portrait": "A/老囚2",
            "position": "right"
        },
        {
            "id": "line_3_6",
            "type": "dialogue",
            "speaker": "B",
            "text": "的确，太多疑点集合在你身上了，后续言语如有冒犯，还请海涵",
            "portrait": "B/盗窃犯2",
            "position": "right"
        },
        {
            "id": "line_3_7",
            "type": "dialogue",
            "speaker": "D",
            "text": "（啧，这下麻烦了）",
            "portrait": "Player/主角1",
            "position": "left"
        },
        {
            "id": "line_3_8",
            "type": "dialogue",
            "speaker": "B",
            "text": "首先请回答，为什么会有十字架项链出现在你的房间里",
            "portrait": "B/盗窃犯",
            "position": "right"
        },
        {
            "id": "line_3_9",
            "type": "dialogue",
            "speaker": "D",
            "text": "（糟了，我现在记忆本来就很混乱，这种情况也没有好的借口）\n（与C相关的宗教物品...每个人的房间都有，或许可以利用这一点）",
            "portrait": "Player/主角1",
            "position": "left"
        },
        {
            "id": "line_3_10",
            "type": "dialogue",
            "speaker": "D",
            "text": "能证明十字架与玩家无关的线索是",
            "portrait": "Player/主角1",
            "position": "left"
        },
        {
            "id": "cmd_RequireEvidence_0",
            "type": "command",
            "command": "RequireEvidence",
            "parameters": [
                "黑皮书",
                "line_3_11",
                "line_3_16"
            ]
        },
        {
            "id": "line_3_11",
            "type": "dialogue",
            "speaker": "D",
            "text": "还解释什么？这根本就不是我的东西",
            "portrait": "Player/主角1",
            "position": "left"
        },
        {
            "id": "line_3_12",
            "type": "dialogue",
            "speaker": "B",
            "text": "....？？",
            "portrait": "B/盗窃犯",
            "position": "right"
        },
        {
            "id": "line_3_13",
            "type": "dialogue",
            "speaker": "D",
            "text": "我和你一样，与C交换。你得到了黑皮书，我得到了项链。\n（说谎）但是不是昨天，因为我也是基督教信徒",
            "portrait": "Player/主角1",
            "position": "left"
        },
        {
            "id": "line_3_14",
            "type": "dialogue",
            "speaker": "A",
            "text": "哈？你什么时候又成基督信徒了？",
            "portrait": "A/老囚2",
            "position": "right"
        },
        {
            "id": "line_3_15",
            "type": "dialogue",
            "speaker": "D",
            "text": "（说谎）我一直都是啊？不然你以为我怎么进来的？",
            "portrait": "Player/主角2",
            "position": "left"
        },
        {
            "id": "cmd_Jump_0",
            "type": "command",
            "command": "Jump",
            "parameters": [
                "line_3_18"
            ]
        },
        {
            "id": "line_3_16",
            "type": "dialogue",
            "speaker": "D",
            "text": "这个理由能说服你们吗",
            "portrait": "Player/主角2",
            "position": "left"
        },
        {
            "id": "line_3_17",
            "type": "dialogue",
            "speaker": "A",
            "text": "你觉得呢？",
            "portrait": "A/老囚2",
            "position": "right"
        },
        {
            "id": "cmd_AddSuspicion_0",
            "type": "command",
            "command": "AddSuspicion",
            "parameters": [
                "D",
                "25"
            ]
        },
        {
            "id": "line_3_18",
            "type": "dialogue",
            "speaker": "A",
            "text": "那..那档案怎么解释，为什么就你一个人的档案是乱码",
            "portrait": "A/老囚1",
            "position": "right"
        },
        {
            "id": "line_3_19",
            "type": "dialogue",
            "speaker": "D",
            "text": "（看来只有我才能看见，该怎么才能蒙混过关？）",
            "portrait": "Player/主角1",
            "position": "left"
        },
        {
            "id": "line_3_20",
            "type": "dialogue",
            "speaker": "D",
            "text": "这你不该问我，典狱长不是在旁边吗？",
            "portrait": "Player/主角2",
            "position": "left"
        },
        {
            "id": "line_3_21",
            "type": "dialogue",
            "speaker": "典狱长",
            "text": "这点我也无法解释，档案不是我写的",
            "portrait": "Warden/典狱长1",
            "position": "center"
        },
        {
            "id": "line_3_22",
            "type": "dialogue",
            "speaker": "B",
            "text": "伪人拥有改变其他人认知的能力，如果你是伪人的话就都说得通了",
            "portrait": "B/盗窃犯2",
            "position": "right"
        },
        {
            "id": "line_3_23",
            "type": "dialogue",
            "speaker": "D",
            "text": "（不好，这样下去对我很不利！）",
            "portrait": "Player/主角1",
            "position": "left"
        },
        {
            "id": "line_3_24",
            "type": "dialogue",
            "speaker": "A",
            "text": "果然就是你把，赶紧投票了！",
            "portrait": "A/老囚1",
            "position": "right"
        },
        {
            "id": "line_3_25",
            "type": "dialogue",
            "speaker": "D",
            "text": "（等等，昨天好像与A打过架，也许可以利用这一点）",
            "portrait": "Player/主角1",
            "position": "left"
        },
        {
            "id": "line_3_26",
            "type": "dialogue",
            "speaker": "D",
            "text": "能证明你不是伪人的证据",
            "portrait": "Player/主角1",
            "position": "left"
        },
        {
            "id": "cmd_RequireEvidence_1",
            "type": "command",
            "command": "RequireEvidence",
            "parameters": [
                "伪人无法抑制杀人冲动",
                "line_3_27",
                "line_3_29"
            ]
        },
        {
            "id": "line_3_27",
            "type": "dialogue",
            "speaker": "D",
            "text": "诸位，我们还记得伪人的特性吗？伪人无法抑制杀人的冲动，假如我真是伪人，某人现在恐怕昨天就被我杀掉了把？\n你看向A",
            "portrait": "Player/主角1",
            "position": "left"
        },
        {
            "id": "line_3_28",
            "type": "dialogue",
            "speaker": "A",
            "text": "......呜",
            "portrait": "A/老囚1",
            "position": "right"
        },
        {
            "id": "cmd_Jump_1",
            "type": "command",
            "command": "Jump",
            "parameters": [
                "line_3_31"
            ]
        },
        {
            "id": "line_3_29",
            "type": "dialogue",
            "speaker": "D",
            "text": "等等，这些足够证明我的清白",
            "portrait": "Player/主角2",
            "position": "left"
        },
        {
            "id": "line_3_30",
            "type": "dialogue",
            "speaker": "典狱长",
            "text": "不，反而成了你在胡编乱造的依据",
            "portrait": "Warden/典狱长1",
            "position": "center"
        },
        {
            "id": "cmd_AddSuspicion_1",
            "type": "command",
            "command": "AddSuspicion",
            "parameters": [
                "D",
                "25"
            ]
        },
        {
            "id": "line_3_31",
            "type": "dialogue",
            "speaker": "D",
            "text": "的确如果你真的是伪人，A是不可能打得过你的",
            "portrait": "Player/主角1",
            "position": "left"
        },
        {
            "id": "line_3_32",
            "type": "dialogue",
            "speaker": "D",
            "text": "刚刚的对话，反而在我的脑海中拼凑出了整个案发过程，让我们继续讨论吧！在到达真理前无法回头",
            "portrait": "Player/主角1",
            "position": "left"
        },
        {
            "id": "line_3_33",
            "type": "dialogue",
            "speaker": "D",
            "text": "我先来还原一下案发过程把\nC离开B房后，像往常一样回房间注射药物，在这期间被伪人杀害",
            "portrait": "Player/主角1",
            "position": "left"
        },
        {
            "id": "line_3_34",
            "type": "dialogue",
            "speaker": "A",
            "text": "我与他无冤无仇，不可能冒险去做这种事",
            "portrait": "A/老囚1",
            "position": "right"
        },
        {
            "id": "line_3_35",
            "type": "dialogue",
            "speaker": "B",
            "text": "的确，除非有死亡笔记，不然很难做到在没有外伤的情况下杀了C",
            "portrait": "B/盗窃犯2",
            "position": "right"
        },
        {
            "id": "line_3_36",
            "type": "dialogue",
            "speaker": "D",
            "text": "我看未必",
            "portrait": "Player/主角1",
            "position": "left"
        },
        {
            "id": "cmd_ShowChoice_0",
            "type": "command",
            "command": "ShowChoice",
            "parameters": [
                "A|line_3_34",
                "B|line_3_42"
            ]
        },
        {
            "id": "line_3_37",
            "type": "dialogue",
            "speaker": "D",
            "text": "你真的干不出来吗？",
            "portrait": "Player/主角1",
            "position": "left"
        },
        {
            "id": "line_3_38",
            "type": "dialogue",
            "speaker": "A",
            "text": "不可能，绝对不可能！我没有杀他的动机",
            "portrait": "A/老囚2",
            "position": "right"
        },
        {
            "id": "line_3_39",
            "type": "dialogue",
            "speaker": "D",
            "text": "A的动机是",
            "portrait": "Player/主角1",
            "position": "left"
        },
        {
            "id": "cmd_RequireEvidence_2",
            "type": "command",
            "command": "RequireEvidence",
            "parameters": [
                "没有喝过的酒",
                "line_3_40",
                "line_3_42"
            ]
        },
        {
            "id": "line_3_40",
            "type": "dialogue",
            "speaker": "D",
            "text": "不，你的动机很纯粹，而且证物就放在你的房间里不是吗\nC先在B房传教，回房间时被喝醉了的你遇到，并与你约定——用卷轴换酒。可C食言了，这就是你的动机",
            "portrait": "Player/主角1",
            "position": "left"
        },
        {
            "id": "line_3_41",
            "type": "dialogue",
            "speaker": "A",
            "text": "什么！！？",
            "portrait": "A/老囚1",
            "position": "right"
        },
        {
            "id": "cmd_AddSuspicion_2",
            "type": "command",
            "command": "AddSuspicion",
            "parameters": [
                "A",
                "25"
            ]
        },
        {
            "id": "cmd_Jump_2",
            "type": "command",
            "command": "Jump",
            "parameters": [
                "line_3_59"
            ]
        },
        {
            "id": "line_3_42",
            "type": "dialogue",
            "speaker": "D",
            "text": "这就是你去C房间的动机",
            "portrait": "Player/主角2",
            "position": "left"
        },
        {
            "id": "line_3_43",
            "type": "dialogue",
            "speaker": "B",
            "text": "没看出来那处是动机",
            "portrait": "B/盗窃犯2",
            "position": "right"
        },
        {
            "id": "line_3_44",
            "type": "dialogue",
            "speaker": "A",
            "text": "耍我呢！",
            "portrait": "A/老囚2",
            "position": "right"
        },
        {
            "id": "cmd_AddSuspicion_3",
            "type": "command",
            "command": "AddSuspicion",
            "parameters": [
                "D",
                "25"
            ]
        },
        {
            "id": "cmd_Jump_3",
            "type": "command",
            "command": "Jump",
            "parameters": [
                "line_3_59"
            ]
        },
        {
            "id": "line_3_45",
            "type": "dialogue",
            "speaker": "D",
            "text": "不，根本就不需要造成外伤，C是看见真主后激动致死",
            "portrait": "Player/主角1",
            "position": "left"
        },
        {
            "id": "line_3_46",
            "type": "dialogue",
            "speaker": "B",
            "text": "什么！？",
            "portrait": "B/盗窃犯",
            "position": "right"
        },
        {
            "id": "line_3_47",
            "type": "dialogue",
            "speaker": "D",
            "text": "能证明激动致死的是",
            "portrait": "Player/主角1",
            "position": "left"
        },
        {
            "id": "cmd_RequireEvidence_3",
            "type": "command",
            "command": "RequireEvidence",
            "parameters": [
                "C的死亡姿势",
                "line_3_48",
                "line_3_56"
            ]
        },
        {
            "id": "line_3_48",
            "type": "dialogue",
            "speaker": "D",
            "text": "C是看见真主后，激动致死",
            "portrait": "Player/主角1",
            "position": "left"
        },
        {
            "id": "line_3_49",
            "type": "dialogue",
            "speaker": "B",
            "text": "搞笑呢？你是说我们当中有天使？",
            "portrait": "B/盗窃犯",
            "position": "right"
        },
        {
            "id": "line_3_50",
            "type": "dialogue",
            "speaker": "D",
            "text": "谁说要是真的了？模仿外貌就可以了",
            "portrait": "Player/主角2",
            "position": "left"
        },
        {
            "id": "line_3_51",
            "type": "dialogue",
            "speaker": "D",
            "text": "有人能改变外貌的证据是",
            "portrait": "Player/主角1",
            "position": "left"
        },
        {
            "id": "cmd_RequireEvidence_4",
            "type": "command",
            "command": "RequireEvidence",
            "parameters": [
                "伪人能改变身体构造",
                "line_3_52",
                "line_3_56"
            ]
        },
        {
            "id": "line_3_52",
            "type": "dialogue",
            "speaker": "D",
            "text": "刚好伪人不就可以改变相貌吗？\n但我们之中昨天见过真主画像的，只有你B",
            "portrait": "Player/主角1",
            "position": "left"
        },
        {
            "id": "line_3_53",
            "type": "dialogue",
            "speaker": "D",
            "text": "只有你昨天看了黑皮书！",
            "portrait": "Player/主角1",
            "position": "left"
        },
        {
            "id": "line_3_54",
            "type": "dialogue",
            "speaker": "B",
            "text": "有趣的思路，我认同凶手的作案手法，但我不是伪人，更不会变成天使。",
            "portrait": "B/盗窃犯2",
            "position": "right"
        },
        {
            "id": "line_3_55",
            "type": "dialogue",
            "speaker": "D",
            "text": "谁信你的鬼话！",
            "portrait": "Player/主角1",
            "position": "left"
        },
        {
            "id": "cmd_AddSuspicion_4",
            "type": "command",
            "command": "AddSuspicion",
            "parameters": [
                "B",
                "25"
            ]
        },
        {
            "id": "cmd_Jump_4",
            "type": "command",
            "command": "Jump",
            "parameters": [
                "line_3_59"
            ]
        },
        {
            "id": "line_3_56",
            "type": "dialogue",
            "speaker": "D",
            "text": "没错就是看见了这些",
            "portrait": "Player/主角2",
            "position": "left"
        },
        {
            "id": "line_3_57",
            "type": "dialogue",
            "speaker": "B",
            "text": "哼哼哼...哈哈哈哈哈哈\n抱歉失态了，我真是高估你了，没想到为了洗脱嫌疑什么都能编得出来",
            "portrait": "B/盗窃犯2",
            "position": "right"
        },
        {
            "id": "line_3_58",
            "type": "dialogue",
            "speaker": "典狱长",
            "text": "够了，不要再胡搅蛮缠",
            "portrait": "Warden/典狱长1",
            "position": "center"
        },
        {
            "id": "cmd_AddSuspicion_5",
            "type": "command",
            "command": "AddSuspicion",
            "parameters": [
                "D",
                "25"
            ]
        },
        {
            "id": "cmd_Jump_5",
            "type": "command",
            "command": "Jump",
            "parameters": [
                "line_3_59"
            ]
        },
        {
            "id": "line_3_59",
            "type": "dialogue",
            "speaker": "典狱长",
            "text": "审判的时钟已经敲响\n刽子手已就绪，该送行了。",
            "portrait": "Warden/典狱长1",
            "position": "center"
        },
        {
            "id": "cmd_LoadEndScene_0",
            "type": "command",
            "command": "LoadEndScene"
        }
    ]
}